{
  "stem": "1885.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 383.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Salto. ?] I don't know how he chose-- chose this name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we took the [? tradotta. ?] The [? tradotta ?] was a train that took Italian soldiers to Athens.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went to Athens with these train with false identity card-- papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were received very warmly in a Greek Christian home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was my father's superior from the factory he used to work to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And his grandson was decorated last year in June because our community decorated and made this special event for the Greeks that helped the Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and he came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was decorated for the-- what his grandfather saved us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, we were on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We didn't have where to live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he took us in his house, the three of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He even found an apartment where we went to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And from there, we went to-- were sent to-- to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With our false identity cards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother and father, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't feel anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was for a trip for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Perhaps it was the first trip for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our belongings were some suitcases.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother tried to put inside the satchel, especially food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- I remember that all the children and myself used to wear this back-- the bags you use now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody wears these bags.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put it on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were-- there was water and food and some cloth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my mother had sewn a ring with a diamond on my shoulder bag-- bag.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a red coat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she had sewn there a ring because you didn't know after the war or doing the war, you didn't have to sell jewelry to save yourself.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
